@node MAINWINDOW "Main Window"

    @{"   " link MAINWINDOWMENU} Menu

    @{FG shine}Results:@{FG text}

    Displayed here are all the results you have entered. DoubleClick on a
    result to open the @{"Edit Window" link EDITWINDOW}. MultiSelect for this list is available
    as default but can be disabled via the @{"Fortune Settings" link FORTUNESETTINGS}. 

    @{FG shine}Add:@{FG text}

    Add an item to the results database.

    @{FG shine}Remove:@{FG text}

    Remove single or multiple items from the results database.

    @{FG shine}Edit:@{FG text}

    Open the @{"Edit Window" link EDITWINDOW} to enter or alter your result.

    @{FG shine}Predict:@{FG text}

    Start the prediction.

    @{FG shine}Prediction Display:@{FG text}

    After processing all your lottery @{"Functions" link FUNCTION}/@{"Methods" link METHOD}, the results will be
    displayed here. The pop-up list button next to the display allows you to
    select which prediction is currently displayed. Click on the prediction to
    access a complete list of predictions and their values.

@endnode

