@node EDITWINDOW "Edit Window"

    @{FG shine}Date:@{FG text}

    Set the date that the lottery took place. If you have entered the
    starting dates of the lottery into the @{"Date Creation" link FORMATSETTINGS 23} section of the
    @{"Format Settings" link FORMATSETTINGS} you should have no need to change this.
    

    @{FG shine}Numbers:@{FG text}

    Just click once on each number in turn to enter a result. The display
    will flash if you try and enter a number that already exists.

    If a result has been entered incorrectly just drag & drop the correct
    number over the result to be altered.

    @{FG shine}Results:@{FG text}

    Either enter the lottery numbers manually or use the number buttons to
    enter the results.

@endnode

@node PREDICTIONWINDOW "Prediction Window"

    The prediction window allows you to see a full list of predictions with
    their respective values allocated by the methods used to select them.

@endnode

@node PRINTWINDOW "Print Window"

    @{FG shine}Select:@{FG text}

    Choose to print results or predictions.

    @{FG shine}Results Options:@{FG text}

    Print all results or only those that you have selected using MultiSelect.

    @{FG shine}Predictions Options:@{FG text}

    Print the names of each @{"method" link METHOD} used in a @{"function" link FUNCTION}.

    @{FG shine}Output:@{FG text}

    Print to a printer or select a file for the data to be written.

    @{FG shine}Proceed:@{FG text}

    Start printing.

@endnode

@node FUNCTIONSWINDOW "Functions Window"

